2026-05-11T07:20:47.5782740Z 13    <!--
2026-05-11T07:20:47.5783340Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-11T07:20:47.5784271Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
